		{
			"title": "商业活动",
			"body": "<p>The official PMI is signalling mild contraction in the crucial manufacturing sphere. Other unofficial PMIs suggest the slowdown is more pronounced. A PMI value of more than 50 indicates expansion. Lower than 50 indicates expected contraction</p>",
